<A>__{a very old car comes coughing in, steam hissing from its engine. helena mahoney, 43, gets out of the driver's seat. her iron will is matched only by her deep reserves of empathy. she gets a good look at the inn. this is what she has come for?}
<L>__{exterior cottage porch day}
<A>__{franklin and roy, having finished lunch, are playing checkers. fred is sitting nearby eating a piece of pie. helena approaches. roy pulls off a triple jump.}
